channel.title: My server wont go online
channel.description:
Hello, I'm finally done with my server so I decided to start hosting.. But I made a IP on no-ip - no-ip.info etc.. No need to PW because I'm not using a router.. But ALL Server checkers keep saying that my server is offline and no one can connect exept me, I can also connect with the ip? :S
Is there anything on my computer that could "block" connection or something? If someone knows, please, help me.
Thanks ~ Extoz.
